Package edu.mit.jwi.dict

Provides the main dictionary interface and a default implementation.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IClassCache  
IClassCacheIDAware Extension of the IClassCache interface that knows how to handle items that implement the IHasID iterface.
IDictionary Objects that implement this interface are intended as the main entry point to accessing the dictionary data.
 

Class Summary
ClassCache Default implementation of the IClassCache interface.
ClassCacheIDAware Default implementation of the IClassCacheIDAware interface.
Dictionary Basic implementation of the IDictionary interface, intended for use with the Wordnet 2.1/3.0 distribution.
StringMatcher A string pattern matcher, suppporting "*" and "?" wildcards.
StringMatcher.Position  
 

Exception Summary
